Sunday dog
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a lazy dog or a dog that responds to commands very quietly and with no fuss.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
